   1:src/usb_audio.c **** // UAC2 stereo capture for GaletSynth â€” see usb_audio.h. Entity IDs (match the
   2:src/usb_audio.c **** // descriptor in usb_descriptors.c): input terminal 1, feature unit 2, output
   3:src/usb_audio.c **** // terminal 3, clock source 4. Async IN endpoint: the device owns the clock and
   4:src/usb_audio.c **** // varies samples/frame (47/48/49) to track it.
