  57:src/usb_audio.c **** // Async IN clock tracking: hold the ring near TARGET frames of latency by sending
  58:src/usb_audio.c **** // 48Â±1 frames/packet. The packet-size variation conveys the device's true rate to
  59:src/usb_audio.c **** // the host, which locks its resampler to it â€” no feedback endpoint needed.
